headline: WITTENSTEIN high integrity systems Announce Strategic Collaboration with Qualcomm to Deliver SAFERTOS® on Snapdragon Digital Chassis Platforms for Automotive Applications
summary: WITTENSTEIN high integrity systems (WHIS), global expert on safety-critical Real Time Operating System (RTOS) technology, is proud to announce its collaboration with Qualcomm Technologies, Inc. This collaboration brings the WHIS SAFERTOS® to the R52 cores of Qualcomm Technologies' Snapdragon® Digital Chassis™ safety island, delivering a high-performance, safety-critical solution for the next generation of automotive applications.
